summary: Weeeey, welcome to the tenth post for the @sciencebrosbingo – Another 2x1 fill, going for the next bingo lines xP Following the...
caption:
Weeeey, welcome to the tenth post for the @sciencebrosbingo – Another 2x1 fill, going for the next bingo lines xP Following the line of things I do, they will have design and text, longer or shorter depending on the moment. All will go under the cut in the posts.

-Hey, Bruce, are you ready?- Tony entered the room where Bruce was changing, who turned quickly to see Tony.
-What are you doing here? Aren’t we supposed to not see each other before the wedding?
-I’m… almost sure that only applies to the dress of the bride… - Tony pointed Bruce and looking at him a little confused, but ended up laughing.- Do you prefer to wear a dress? Or do you want me to wear a dress?
-No, no… your suit is… perfect … - Bruce barely came to notice this one.
-Same as yours.- Tony moved closer to Bruce. -So… Are you ready? The guests have been waiting for a while. After all, a Stark-Banner wedding is not something that is held every day, although if you want more than one wedding, it’s something we could talk about.
-And if now I get to say ‘no’ when they ask me if I want to marry you?
-Oh, Brucie Bear, I know you will not be able to say it as soon as you look at me.

They both laughed, but yes, it was time to complete the circle, start a new life, both as a married couple.

summary: Ok so I realized something about pepper*ny that has been really bugging me since I first noticed it: Has Pepper actually done...
body:
Ok so I realized something about pepper*ny that has been really bugging me since I first noticed it: Has Pepper actually done anything nice for Tony or even just said something nice about him? I’m genuinely asking. Literally the only thing I can think of is the “Proof Tony Stark has a heart” gift in IM1.

Tony is constantly gushing about her, complimenting her and bringing up how important she is to him.

he made her CEO, used the iron man suit to give her a massage when she came home from work, gotten her gifts and, just to make her happy, he destroyed the suits (something that means the world to him)

Now sure there’s a hug or her calling him “honey” or something now and then but a large chunk of the time she’s just irritated with him & goes on about how frustrating being with him is
